<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<game romname="roadblst" gamename="Road Blasters (upright, rev 4)" numPlayers="1" alternating="0" mirrored="0" usesService="0" tilt="0" cocktail="0">
	<miscDetails>
Steering wheel is unique in that it uses optics but is restricted to ~270 degrees, and it returns to the center position using springs.     Also, it has 2 triggers (Fire Lasers), and 2 thumb buttons (Activate Special Weapon).  Each trigger / thumb button does the same action.  
	</miscDetails>
	<player number="1" numButtons="2">
		<controls>
			<control name="Pedal (Analog)">
				<constant name="pedal"/>
			</control>
			<control name="360 Steering Wheel">
				<constant name="dial"/>
				<button name="P1_BUTTON1"/>
				<button name="P1_BUTTON2"/>
			</control>
			<control name="Misc">
				<constant name="other"/>
			</control>
		</controls>
	<labels>
			<label name="P1_BUTTON1" value="Fire Lasers"/>
			<label name="P1_BUTTON2" value="Activate Special Weapon"/>
			<label name="P1_DIAL_EXT" value="Right"/>
			<label name="P1_DIAL" value="Left"/>
			<label name="P1_PEDAL" value="Accelerate"/>
		</labels>
	</player>
</game>
